text: ADAAAAMMMM I asked you to apply on the 26th Jan! C'mon man, lemme see that sweet sweet cover letter!!!!

Awwwwwww, I'm so sorry :sob:
I didn't want to disappoint you! I thought that there was no time limit for this task. I even checked the previous messages. Cos I thought, maybe I just missed any dates or just didn't notice. But I didn't find any.

Still, I'm sorry. I'll finish and send it to you tomorrow. Thank you for reminding.
Sometimes I need, what I call, "holy kick". That mobilise me rapidly :smile:
